TextEng: You're Revat's Momma right? I am here to rescue you.
You can stop worrying. I'm here to rescue you.
You are free to go, but not with me. You can leave on your own.
Text: 이제 가도 돼. 근데 나랑은 못 가. 혼자 나가.

TextEng: Just stay right there and don't move. I'll be back.
You Revat's Momma? Me here save you.
You be happy. Me free you.
You be free, but no follow me.
Text: 너 자유야. 근데 나 따라오지 마.

TextEng: You don't move. I'll be back.
Sorry, he never said your name.
Text: 미안, 그 사람이 이름은 안 알려줬거든.

TextEng: Since I am here to rescue you, you might want to be more polite.
Text: 구하러 온 건데 좀 예의 있게 굴지 그래.

TextEng: Him never tell me you name.
Text: 그 사람 나한테 이름 안 알려줬어.

TextEng: You be nice, since me free you.
Text: 나 너 풀어줄 거야. 착하게 해.

TextEng: So how am I supposed to help you?
What do you expect me to do about it?
So what me do to help?
What you think me can do to fix you mistake?
Are you always this miserable?
So why didn't they kill you, or eat you?
Text: 근데 왜 죽이거나 잡아먹지 않은 거야?

TextEng: Why they not kill and eat you?
You always so grumpy?
The others were attacked by the trolls and ogres, right?
Text: 다른 사람들은 트롤이랑 오우거한테 습격당한 거지?

TextEng: So what did you do?
Them attacked by trolls 'n' ogres?
What you do then?
Could you explain what happened to you again?
You can come with me now.
You're just not worth rescuing. Goodbye.
Text: 구해줄 맛이 안 나네. 잘 있어.

TextEng: How you get here again?
Me go now, you follow.
Me not want to rescue you. Bye.
I am clearing the trolls and ogres out of these caves. Who are you and why are you here?
Text: 이 동굴에서 트롤이랑 오우거를 소탕하고 있어. 넌 누구고 왜 여기 있는 거야?

TextEng: Me kill bad trolls 'n' ugly ogres. Who you and why you here?
Text: 나 나쁜 트롤이랑 못생긴 오우거 죽여. 너 누구고 왜 여기 있어?

TextEng: So what happened?
Is this story going to take much longer?
That bad. What next?
You get to point soon.
A goddess? Why do you think that?
Somebody's going senile, I think.
Text: 누가 머리가 좀 이상해진 것 같은데.

TextEng: Why them think you goddess?
You go crazy, maybe?
Where would I find your son?
I'm busy now, but maybe later.
Where me find you son?
Me busy. Maybe me do later.
Okay. Where would I find your son.
Sorry. Maybe someone else will come along.
Okay. Where me find son?
Me gotta go. Bye.
How will it do that?
All right, here's the ring.
I've changed my mind. I think I'll keep the ring.
How it do that?
Okay, here be you ring.
Me not want give you ring. Me keep.
Text: 반지 안 줄래. 내가 가질 거야.

TextEng: No. I will keep it and you will die. Goodbye.
Text: 싫어. 내가 가지고 넌 죽어. 안녕.

TextEng: Nope. Me keep. Bye.
What do you mean 'kind of' a prisoner?
Well, the trolls guarding you are dead, so you can go.
Text: 지키던 트롤들 다 죽었으니까 이제 가도 돼.

TextEng: What you mean by that?
Them trolls be dead. You free now.
I kill da trolls, so you be safe to leave now.
Text: 나 트롤 죽였어. 이제 안전하게 나가.

TextEng: You no need help find way out?
The way back is cleared of trolls; find your own way out.
Text: 돌아가는 길에 트롤은 없어. 알아서 나가.

TextEng: Don't you need help getting back to Revat?
Text: 레바트한테 돌아가는 거 도움 필요 없어?
